This Friday (2 June, 7pm), Tullis Rennie closes this year's <a href="http://instagram.com/CitySummerSounds">@CitySummerSounds</a> festival with "Expanding Fixed Freedoms", a live reimagining of his recent release on
@accidental_jnr records. Tullis' "unpredictable analogue circuits" will be augmented by four outstanding, improvising live musicians: Preetha Narayanan, Tara Franks, Cath Roberts & Dee Byrne.

Free to attend! Details and booking forms for all our concert events are here: www.city.ac.uk/music-events
